### [seprocess](file:///c:/Users/Glauber/codes/MicroTaskManager/seprocess)

#### [MODIFY] [quality-gates-template.md](file:///c:/Users/Glauber/codes/MicroTaskManager/seprocess/quality-gates-template.md)
Finalize thresholds for Python tools.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `pytest` for functional API testing.
- `ruff check .` for linting.
- `mypy .` for type consistency.
- `pylint --disable=all --enable=similarities .` for duplication check.

### Manual Verification
- Access `/docs` (Swagger) to verify the "WOW Factor" and test endpoints manually.
